# Important

## Notifications
Use the CLI `notify <message>` to notify the user.

## Contributing Code

1. Try keeping things as simple as possible, but no simpler.
2. Favor functions over classes.
3. Follow established codebase patterns.

## Obsidian Vault

When writing a report use the report-writing skill to write to the
Obsidian vault located at /home/hdemers/Dropbox/Documents/Obsidian/Grubhub/
(or might also be under /var/home/hdemers/...)

